version_description: Follows song's original chords. Song is found here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RsaK6p8HDnU . Capo 2.
The song is really about 3 simple chords. If you wish, you could trasnpose it 2 semitones lower (Em, C, G respectively) and put a capo on a 2 fret.
I did this version with Capo on 1st fret because chords are much simple. Hope you'll like it (:.

Okay, so this is my first tab and I played this song by ear. And I just made up my own pattern for this song, so you can play it any way you want. And I apologize if there are mistakes in this song, but it sounds pretty accurate, I hope you like it.
